features: 【Designed for RTX 3090 Ti / 4070 Ti / 4080 / 4090】ATX 3.0 PCIe 5.0 12+4pin 12VHPWR 90 Degree Angled Adapter is designed for GeForce RTX 3090Ti 4070 Ti 4080 4090 GPU, This one is Type B, Please check the product picture and orientation of your GPU before purchasing

【90 Degree 16Pin (12+4) Pin Adapter 】90 Degree Angle allows to work with your original power cable, and have a suitable extension direction, which can avoid the wear of the cable and the input port of GPU, extend the service life,this sepcial design is more flexible than normal adapters

【Supports up to 600W, 16AWG Tinned Copper Wire】The adapter is without PCB board, which is more stable and has better heat heat dissipation, supports maximum power output of 600W,and please assure your power cable is 600W
【Note】Please refer to product description as well as the chosen variant to ensure compatibility with your graphics card before purchasing.
Package Include:1PCS 16(12+4) Pin 90 Degree Adapter (Type B)
